import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from scipy.signal import argrelextrema
from feature_functions import *
from tqdm import tqdm

# load the CSV file
data = pd.read_csv('C:/Users/diego.bettega/Desktop/PROJECT 4/Dataset/EURUSD.csv')
data = data.iloc[1000:10000]
data.columns = ['Date','open','high','low','close','volume']
data = data.set_index(pd.to_datetime(data.Date))
data = data[['open','high','low','close','volume']]
data = data.drop_duplicates(keep=False)
prices = data.close.copy()


# Find harmonic patterns
err_allowed = 10.0/100
count = 0
pips = np.zeros(15)

pnl = []
trade_dates = []
correct_pats = 0
pats = 0
plt.ion()

for i in (range(100,len(prices.values))):
    current_idx,current_pat,start,end = peaks_detect(prices.values[:i],order=5)
    
    XA = current_pat[1] - current_pat[0]
    AB = current_pat[2] - current_pat[1]
    BC = current_pat[3] - current_pat[2]
    CD = current_pat[4] - current_pat[3]
    
    moves = [XA,AB,BC,CD]
    
    gartley = is_gartley(moves,err_allowed)
    butterfly = is_butterfly(moves,err_allowed)
    but = is_but(moves,err_allowed)
    crab = is_crab(moves,err_allowed)
    
    harmonics = np.array([gartley,butterfly,but,crab])
    labels = ['Gartley','Butterfly','But','Crab']
    
    if np.any(harmonics == 1) or np.any(harmonics == -1):
        for j in range(0,len(harmonics)):
            if harmonics[j] == 1 or harmonics[j] == -1:
                pats += 1
                sense = 'Bearish ' if harmonics[j] == -1 else 'Bullish '
                label = sense + labels[j] + ' Found'
                
                start = np.array(current_idx).min()
                end = np.array(current_idx).max()
                date = data.iloc[end].name
                trade_dates = np.append(trade_dates,date)
                
                pips = walk_forward(prices.values[end:],harmonics[j],slippage=4,stop=5)
                pnl = np.append(pnl,pips)
                cumpips = pnl.cumsum()
                
                if pips>0:
                    correct_pats +=1
                lbl = 'Accuracy' + str(round(100*float(correct_pats)/float(pats),2)) + '%'
                print('Pips Trade = '+str(round(10000*pips,2)))
                print('Total = '+str(round(10000*cumpips[-1],2)))
                
                plt.title(label)
                plt.plot(np.arange(start,i+15),prices.values[start:i+15])
                plt.plot(current_idx,current_pat,c='r')
                plt.show()
                plt.clf()
                plt.plot(cumpips,label=lbl)
                plt.legend()
                plt.show()
